Install ubuntu on thinkpad
- Ubuntu 22.04
- Wayland (Not XWindowServer)

1. Optimize trackpoint (Wayland)
   (https://rabexc.org/posts/carbon-x1-trackpad)
   mkdir -p /etc/libinput
   cat > /etc/libinput/local-overrides.quirks <<END
   [Trackpoint Override]
   MatchUdevType=pointingstick
   AttrTrackpointMultiplier=0.55
   END

1. Change Keymap
  1) Capslock -> Ctrl
  2) ESC <-> `

1. Resolve dmesg fail

1. Finger print detecting
